<item>
            <title>[LU-3634] Bad returned code on error for llapi_hsm_copy_start/end()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3634</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When an &lt;tt&gt;ioctl()&lt;/tt&gt; returns an error, the error code is in &lt;tt&gt;errno&lt;/tt&gt;, not in &lt;tt&gt;rc&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;llapi_hsm_copy_start()&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;llapi_hsm_copy_end()&lt;/tt&gt; should return &lt;tt&gt;errno&lt;/tt&gt; in these cases instead of ioctl &lt;tt&gt;rc&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
